Renders property value rows for a SemanticSchemas category display.

Discovers all properties (including inherited) by walking the ancestor
chain via Category/collect-ancestors, querying Property field subobjects
on each ancestor category, then rendering a table row for each property
whose value is non-empty on the target page.

Parameters:
* category - The category name (without namespace prefix)
* page - The page (or subobject fragment, e.g. "ParentPage#_hash")
         to read property values from. Defaults to {{FULLPAGENAME}},
         making this template usable both for the current page and
         for rendering subobject instances via Category/subobject-instance.
</noinclude>
